<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>WE'LL MEET EACH OTHER THERE!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nisa hung tum pai tan tin,
 I nasep I zawh tieng leh;
 I lunggim nau cheng hung bei ta'na,
 Mahleh Lei leh Van Lalpa'n;
 Ei uh ei hungpui intin,
 Zion tangah kituok khawm hitiu.

[V2]
 Zie chun kituok hitiu,
 Zie chun kituok khawm hitiu;
 Hukdampa batna nei in
 Zie gam vak leh hawih achun;
 Zie chun kituok hitiu,
 Ziechun kituok khawm hitiu;
 A lopina chang tai tiu.

[V3]
 2. Luiguom a thimnuoi achun,
 Huihhat nun git chuh lau in;
 Thimna leh huih pin ei um kimvel,
 Mahleh gamvak nuom achun;
 Lalpan ei puitung intin,
 Leichung huihpi nunna khel achun.

[V4]
 3. I mitthiu chuh luong henla,
 I lung lauhna'n dim mahleh;
 Leichung nite buoina'n dim mahleh,
 I Lalpau chuh hung intin,
 A In a eipui ding in,
 Zie chun lungkhamna um ta puo'n a.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>405</hymn_number>
</song>